# Database Access with Drizzle

All **database interactions** in this project must use the **Drizzle schema and queries** defined in
[`src/db/schema.ts`](mdc:src/db/schema.ts).

- **Do not** write raw SQL queries directly in application code.
- **Do not** create ad-hoc table definitions outside the Drizzle schema.
- **Always**:
  - Use the tables and types exported from [`src/db/schema.ts`](mdc:src/db/schema.ts).
  - Add or update table definitions in [`src/db/schema.ts`](mdc:src/db/schema.ts) when the schema changes.

This ensures a single source of truth for the database schema and keeps all queries type-safe and consistent.
